article_title: Senior Hamas official says deaths of leaders not 'the end of our movement'
sentence: Hamas  Political  Bureau  member,  Basem  Naim,  has  released  a  statement  saying:  "It  seems  that  Israel  believes  that  killing  our  leaders  means  the  end  of  our  movement  and  the  struggle  of  the  Palestinian  people.  "
